reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 121/01: DESIGNATION OF PARTICIPATING MUNICIPALITY AND NUMBER OF MEMBERS APPOINTED
reg_info.reg_name_text: DESIGNATION OF PARTICIPATING MUNICIPALITY AND NUMBER OF MEMBERS APPOINTED
reg_info.act_under: St. Clair Parks Commission Act, 2000   Loi de 2000 sur la Commission des parcs de la Sainte-Claire

content.content: 1. The County of Lambton is designated as a participating municipality. O. Reg. 121/01, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. The County of Lambton is designated as a participating municipality. O. Reg. 121/01, s. 1.

content.content: 2. The County of Lambton may appoint four members to the Commission. O. Reg. 121/01, s. 2.
content.raw_html: 2. The County of Lambton may appoint four members to the Commission. O. Reg. 121/01, s. 2.
